brief.brief: The Change category that will be used when a Subscription cancelation is requested for this Business Service.

detail.detail: This selection is only used when the Subscription cancelation request is being handled directly by Change Management without the use of Service Catalog. Otherwise, the Service Catalog connector determines how a Subscription is added and fulfilled.
